Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.96,0:11:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得把衣服收进来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你去哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子已经没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之快点给我收进来！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  阪本先生  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这雨下得真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服有帮我收进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为阪本要我收进去的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦  真的是阪本说要我收进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为阪本先生说要收进去  然后衣服就掉下来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啦  阪本先生说收进去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后说把衣服弄掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  吓死我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞎说什么啊  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是那样说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有说「把衣服弄掉下来」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有说！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  就把阪本当做祭品来补偿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:12:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:12:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了啦  衣服脏了洗一下就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的也对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天这样的已经无法挽回了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的晚饭你们俩都不准吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  为什么要牵连我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是这是阪本犯的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把阪本当做祭品来补偿就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  那么我就收下阪本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只不准博士吃晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啦  那么就让博士来当祭品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为把衣服弄掉的是博士  把衣服弄得湿湿的也是博士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:41.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵  今天的晚饭是蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为鸡蛋很便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  博士今天不是不能吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛…算了  总之今天就让你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  太好了  太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就不准你吃了
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水  水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲨鱼鲨鱼  啪咔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲨鱼鲨鱼  啪库
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Selamat pagi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘土自塑像的作业你们不觉得超麻烦的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  那个作业今天要交吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧咧  美绪老师  莫非您忘记了喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为是明天交啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣你做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连麻衣都没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子要下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是下雨能形容的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要天变地异了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天变地异…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:15.86,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,300)\fad(400,00)}日\N常\N之\N81
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要对我的寺庙做什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些香火钱小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:08.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}希望世界和平
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒旦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘟神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我的寺庙里滚出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「走下去吧！」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们这样想着  任凭晚秋的雨打在身上
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:15.39,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(400,00)}日\N常\N之\N82
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您了  部长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.83,0:18:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我要和高崎老师决胜  能请您来当裁判吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指围棋足球的裁判吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  如果我获胜的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师会二话不说来当顾问的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能成功的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我之前借你的「围棋足球入门」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看过那个就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没看入门书是我的不对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这两人从刚才开始在做什么  我完全搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是围棋足球！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你看了入门书也不会懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小木
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:19:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两人可谓是一开始就使出了禁招的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说是理论上的至高等级攻防
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如那笔直的手  如果把那比作围棋盘的腿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手的那个架势就是棋子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乍一看他俩很和谐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从他脚上夹着的球来看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的推测  他们两人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会成为太阳的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么我完全不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Charge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be Loved
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小木  那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这两人之间流动着紧绷的空气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是乱来的话   会有人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:20:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是很久没有看到这样高等级的比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得连风都变得躁动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  这个姿势是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.83,0:20:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在非正式比赛中使出那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这状况  可不能放着不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲  请允许我使出那招
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是为了正义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为放射光芒的星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小木禁招流超奥义之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小木星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是  「Ahh Final loved」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不赖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我以轻松的心情创造的社团
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.74,0:21:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又变成了不得了的事情了
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
